{"tid":2238960,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"廖慧儀男友凌晨自爆慘被狠飛　女方IG已將昔日甜蜜放閃合照全刪走","createTime":"2020-10-11T14:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T08:44:59.000Z","uid":101341,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9b729d0c3bc870343079401e5e3fe647d284fc37","tid":2238960,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"男友Sam於深夜上載兩人曾經甜蜜的合照，卻留下傷心的句子，內容如下：「同你一齊呢一年半，大大小小傷心既事我都陪你經歷過，係你有低潮困難嘅時候，我從來無離開過你身邊，而點會你要選擇咁樣對我，去報答我一年半對你嘅所有付出，我一直當你係一家人，點解要選擇因為1d小問題，而突然狠心離開我？係咪因為入咗娛樂圈，擴闊咗眼界，回頭看所有嘢覺得我甚麼都不是？」言行間似是被冠上莫須有罪名的Sam，直言覺得女友入娛樂圈後為人變了，更似是若有所指，暗示女友找到另一個更有將來的碼頭，而離他而去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/212572/2020%E8%90%BD%E9%81%B8%E6%B8%AF%E5%A7%90-%E5%BB%96%E6%85%A7%E5%84%80%E7%96%91%E6%B4%BE%E5%B8%BD%E6%90%AD%E4%B8%8A-%E7%BF%BB%E7%89%88%E7%BE%85%E4%BB%B2%E8%AC%99-%E6%AD%A3%E5%8D%B0%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87-%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E7%8B%A0%E5%BF%83%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%88%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F212572%2F2020%25E8%2590%25BD%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A7%2590-%25E5%25BB%2596%25E6%2585%25A7%25E5%2584%2580%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B8%25BD%25E6%2590%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A-%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E7%2589%2588%25E7%25BE%2585%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25AC%2599-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%258D%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%25A4%259C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2596%2587-%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2584%25B6%25E7%258B%25A0%25E5%25BF%2583%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2588%2591&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=5c5a9952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/212572/2020%E8%90%BD%E9%81%B8%E6%B8%AF%E5%A7%90-%E5%BB%96%E6%85%A7%E5%84%80%E7%96%91%E6%B4%BE%E5%B8%BD%E6%90%AD%E4%B8%8A-%E7%BF%BB%E7%89%88%E7%BE%85%E4%BB%B2%E8%AC%99-%E6%AD%A3%E5%8D%B0%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87-%E7%AA%81%E7%84%